sequenceDiagram
    actor Presenter
    participant Copilot as NetBox Copilot
    participant NB as NetBox Cloud
    participant EDA as EDA Event Stream
    participant AAP as AAP Controller
    participant VE as Visual Explorer
    participant RS as Report Server

    Presenter->>Copilot: "IPLC-GB-PH-PRI has failed —\nset it to deprovisioning"
    Copilot->>NB: PATCH /circuits/circuits/{id}/\nstatus → deprovisioning
    NB-->>Copilot: 200 OK
    NB->>EDA: Webhook POST\n{model: circuit, cid: IPLC-GB-PH-PRI,\nstatus: deprovisioning}
    EDA->>AAP: run_job_template\nfailed_circuit=IPLC-GB-PH-PRI
    Note over AAP: Query NetBox for backup circuit
    AAP->>NB: GET circuits between GB-Bristol ↔ PH-Manila-01
    NB-->>AAP: IPLC-GB-PH-SEC (Meridian, 1 Gbps)
    Note over AAP: Simulate router config push
    AAP->>NB: PATCH IPLC-GB-PH-PRI → deprovisioning
    AAP->>NB: PATCH IPLC-GB-PH-SEC → active
    AAP->>RS: Upload failover_report.html
    NB->>VE: Live map update\n(failed circuit removed)
    Presenter->>VE: "Circuit line is gone from the map"
    Presenter->>RS: Open report URL
    Note over RS: Report shows failed/backup,\nrouters, timeline, ROI
